822433.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (72.28 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 19:38&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32008157&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1281414120689f988befd800_54958412"/><published>2025-08-15T19:38:18+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>450c45af729fd8fb513f6c510922029e</id><title>騙貸三千萬跑路美國開酒吧，銀行下跪求還債，現實比電影還魔幻。。</title><updated>2025-08-15T20:41:02+08:00</updated><author><name>流西水股</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-15T20:41:02+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573613660"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573613660"&gt;你有沒有想過，普通人欠銀行兩萬塊，催收電話打到你懷疑人生，甚至半夜都能被吓醒。可有些人，欠銀行三千多萬，居然能在美國過成“人生贏家”？今天這個事兒，真的是讓人氣笑了。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434120" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_3210fdf350ed785effe4gggAAJe3FiBb.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d8f9ae/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_3210fdf350ed785effe4gggAAJe3FiBb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434120_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434120&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261657724.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (191.5 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;欠錢跑了，居然成了“座上賓”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;事情的主角叫蔣太子，混跡短視頻圈的網紅，表面上風風火火，背地裡一通操作，把銀行玩得團團轉。你說他本事吧，確實有點。人家一邊在國內高調融資，搞了個3980萬的大項目，另一邊，直接把上海的兩套房掛出去賣了，2300萬現金轉移到國外。你以為他是跑路？錯，他是“升級打怪”去了美國。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434121" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_eb9340dd9b564abfeb4cBkbAzSeMLX0N.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/ab93f4/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_eb9340dd9b564abfeb4cBkbAzSeMLX0N.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434121_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434121&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261657799.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (171.41 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;到了美國，人家日子過得比在國內還嗨。買別墅、開酒吧，六家酒吧輪流轉場，帶娃去加拿大讀書，朋友圈晒得都是“人生贏家劇本”。說實話，我看的時候，腦子裡就冒出一個詞：囂張！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434122" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_e63f8da5497689ca6e60kKkIZENDOCEX.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/5a2c0a/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_e63f8da5497689ca6e60kKkIZENDOCEX.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434122_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434122&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261657854.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (184.6 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434123" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_9844a6cf362b9b94aa24mKVwCzJmzBQt.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/695db4/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_9844a6cf362b9b94aa24mKVwCzJmzBQt.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434123_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434123&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261657906.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (240.12 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;銀行的臉，真是被踩在地上摩擦&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;你以為銀行會坐視不理？當然不！但你猜怎么着，銀行的操作堪比大型“社死”現場。蔣太子剛一跑路，銀行那邊急得上躥下跳，行長親自出馬，連利息都不要了，3180萬本金也願意給你打九折，甚至保證“不追究法律責任”。哇，這待遇，普通人想都不敢想吧？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434124" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_983553e80d68b82bed47zU2miTltQoe5.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/783c03/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_983553e80d68b82bed47zU2miTltQoe5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434124_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434124&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261657958.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (213.52 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;更誇張的是，銀行人員各種低聲下氣，生怕得罪了“太子爺”，生怕這錢徹底收不回來。你說這不是現實版的“欠錢的才是大爺”嗎？而且蔣太子根本不鳥他們，說得很直接——要不你把公司和車子拍賣了，要不你去美國法院告我。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434125" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_0aea4825344b5cec29bdeXa51CLZFR7H.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a6fd6f/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_0aea4825344b5cec29bdeXa51CLZFR7H.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434125_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434125&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261658007.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (166.47 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;欠得多，反倒沒人敢動你？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;這事要擱在我們身上，估計早就被催得生活不能自理了。可蔣太子呢？照樣逍遙法外。他的公司本來就是個“殼”，最多加上車子也就值個五十萬，但銀行居然信了他的“大餅”，把三千多萬砸給他。現在出事了，銀行開始各種“放水”，能免的都給你免了，就差沒磕頭認錯了。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;最讓我無語的是，銀行內部還不敢把這事上報總部，怕被查出來全體下崗。你說這算誰的鍋？一邊是監管不嚴，一邊是內部有人走後門，最后倒霉的是誰？普通儲戶的錢，被人家拿去瀟洒了。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434126" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_a4585f3800ea790e5737DUeHV4qyvptb.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e79f8b/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_a4585f3800ea790e5737DUeHV4qyvptb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434126_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434126&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261658043.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (117.39 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;你以為國外就是天堂？真以為風頭能一直過？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有的人看到這裡，可能會覺得——哇，原來只要跑得快，錢就能永遠花下去？別做夢了兄弟，現在全球打擊“跑路老賴”可是越來越狠。中國這幾年跨國追債、資產凍結的案例多了去了，別看蔣太子現在風光，真要哪天國際通緝令下來，分分鐘照樣得回國喝茶。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434127" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_76a47778c5c8694d1e1fEylWwPW1Dfk0.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/ccb5e2/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_76a47778c5c8694d1e1fEylWwPW1Dfk0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434127_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434127&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261658077.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (216.53 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;更搞笑的是，這事鬧大后，居然還有電商請他去直播帶貨，簡直讓人哭笑不得。銀行都被他“玩弄于鼓掌之間”，電商敢跟他玩，不怕哪天自己也被收拾了？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16434128" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573613660" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_fc413f1093dabc4325ddo4GwEKyeiRQD.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/fa9dc1/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250815/20250815_fc413f1093dabc4325ddo4GwEKyeiRQD.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16434128_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16434128&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1755261658150.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (107 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-15 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;這鍋，最后還是咱們老百姓背&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;說到底，蔣太子只是個“聰明的老賴”，本事再大，也不過是鑽了制度的空子。真正可氣的是，銀行層層把關，居然能讓這種人輕鬆過關，背后肯定不是一個人的問題。普通人還在為幾千塊貸款愁眉苦臉，有些人卻能拿着幾千萬“換個賽道”繼續瀟洒，想想真讓人生氣。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;而且這種事要是成了風氣，吃虧的永遠是咱們這些老實人。銀行的錢不是天上掉下來的，最后賠進去的，還是我們自己的存款。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;蔣太子的故事，怎么看怎么像一出黑色幽默。欠了銀行三千多萬跑國外，反倒成了人生贏家，銀行行長都快“求他還錢”了。這事要擱電影裡，肯定被罵狗血劇情，可現實就這么魔幻。只能說，欠錢的永遠是大爺，欠多了更是“太爺”。但別以為能一直逍遙，風頭遲早會過去，賬也遲早要算。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;你身邊有見過這樣“囂張”的老賴嗎？你覺得銀行該不該這么“低聲下氣”？歡迎留言，一起聊聊！&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32008200&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1281414120689f988befd800_54958412"/><published>2025-08-15T20:41:02+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>7014cb60670e6e439753cc9879ae5287</id><title>北角特賣場結業潮3間執2間網民歸咎淘多多老闆︰內地網購打擊</title><updated>2025-08-13T10:01:47+08:00</updated><author><name>kamao2011</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-13T10:01:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573581111"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573581111"&gt;【淘寶／拼多多／淘多多／結業／執笠／降級消費】代表「降級消費」的特賣場也結業。近港鐵北角站出口的昌明洋樓一段約50米長路段，5間面向英皇道舖&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573581111" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_1058a89d9214e89c984cQRwpzavVcLwi.jpeg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_1058a89d9214e89c984cQRwpzavVcLwi.jpeg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/0991c2/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_1058a89d9214e89c984cQRwpzavVcLwi.jpeg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;大量香港人逃稅&lt;br/&gt;唔交地產稅高官稅&lt;br/&gt;香港衙門債台高築&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新聞來源連結:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/60265944/%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%89%B9%E8%B3%A3%E5%A0%B4%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E6%BD%AE3%E9%96%93%E5%9F%B72%E9%96%93-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%AD%B8%E5%92%8E%E6%B7%98%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%9A-%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A?utm_medium=Social&amp;amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;amp;fbclid=IwQ0xDSwMI0ORleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHhmxu6CrZ2oAqnA2H0ZoNgiq4RGTXeNUq_quF7PGcd2tRBcs9A1cvpji-2Us_aem_9BB2BqKXke8ae4g-G9PZqg" target="_blank" uhash="0d04a5a2331339e598d834477192b376"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/60265944/北角特賣場結業潮3間執2間-網民歸咎淘多多-老闆-內地網購打擊?utm_medium=Social&amp;amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;amp;fbclid=IwQ0xDSwMI0ORleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHhmxu6CrZ2oAqnA2H0ZoNgiq4RGTXeNUq_quF7PGcd2tRBcs9A1cvpji-2Us_aem_9BB2BqKXke8ae4g-G9PZqg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32006033&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1101&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-08-13T10:01:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3757662d36bbd2297ef3f60f63a4a56e</id><title>結業潮│黃大仙藥房稱執笠貼大字賣慘：五雷轟頂謎樣告示成焦點</title><updated>2025-08-13T15:30:54+08:00</updated><author><name>kwoklso6</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-13T15:30:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573585054"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573585054"&gt;【結業潮 / 執笠潮】香港近期結業潮一浪接一浪，甚至連藥房都捱不住經濟寒冬。近日網上流傳帖文，顯示黃大仙1間藥房宣布「執笠」，店內店外貼出許&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_3a74072a0c1abd06cee9sIlN7ax0XLs3.jpeg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_3a74072a0c1abd06cee9sIlN7ax0XLs3.jpeg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f19aa3/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250813/20250813_3a74072a0c1abd06cee9sIlN7ax0XLs3.jpeg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/FZpDTfj.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/FZpDTfj.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f3be11/f/800x0/https://iili.io/FZpDTfj.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/FZpDu0x.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/FZpDu0x.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/10f37a/f/800x0/https://iili.io/FZpDu0x.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/FZpDzib.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/FZpDzib.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c74375/f/800x0/https://iili.io/FZpDzib.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/108bf4/f/320x0/https://i.imgflip.com/a2oq8o.gif" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/108bf4/f/320x0/https://i.imgflip.com/a2oq8o.gif" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/108bf4/f/320x0/https://i.imgflip.com/a2oq8o.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/2iOMnEX.md.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/2iOMnEX.md.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/16d6b5/f/800x0/https://iili.io/2iOMnEX.md.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/2wM3ILX.md.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/2wM3ILX.md.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7a91c4/f/800x0/https://iili.io/2wM3ILX.md.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.5rem"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;超哥話無問題!&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="66" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_o12.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573585054" original-img="https://iili.io/FZynwWG.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://iili.io/FZynwWG.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d675e9/f/800x0/https://iili.io/FZynwWG.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新聞來源連結:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.hk01.com/article/60265980?utm_medium=referral&amp;amp;utm_source=01appshare" target="_blank" uhash="664ec32ca145fb7362f85aca3e5fd048"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/60265980?utm_medium=referral&amp;amp;utm_source=01appshare&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32006252&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1101&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-08-13T15:30:54+08:00</published></entry></feed>